data.description: Welcome to your dream home in sought after Fort Zumwalt District! This striking 3 bedroom ranch in serene location is the epitome of comfort and style. The moment you pull up you will fall in love with the large lot with meticulous landscaping and curb appeal. The moment you enter you’ll be greeted by gleaming real wood flooring and large inviting open floor plan along with vaulted ceiling and unique wood burning fireplace as the focal point. The brand new kitchen is a must see with custom cabinets and counter tops and brand new stainless steel appliances. The cozy master suite and 2 additional spacious bedrooms complete the main level. Downstairs is perfect for entertaining with large rec room and 2 additional sleeping areas along with full bath! The backyard is on oversized 1/3 are level lot and has endless potential! Quiet street and neighborhood with no HOA!
